chedObjectBase) other).position == this.position;\n    }\n\n    public int hashCode() {\n        return (int) position;\n    }\n\n    public void restore() {}\n\n    public void destroy() {}\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777432869472}}
